stories.text:
I see a lot of non-fiction recommendations that are mostly generalizations about something and references to source material they researched, and they turn out to be pretty hollow in terms of reading.

However, books that have been written by people who have worked years in that field or on that topic have mostly been a good experience.

Looking for some more of those types of books
stories.title: Ask HN: Non-fiction books written by people with lots of experience in the field
